parameters:
\N<Kaede>Back when we played hide and seek, you cheated and hid here,
didn't you?
\N<Naoto>But, if we talk to those two, they'll understand...

\N<Miya>Th-That's not possible! Those two are rumored to be trouble
even in the town I used to live in.... If we get caught up with them,
who knows what will happen....

\N<Kaede>Why would you get involved with someone like her, knowing
she's his girlfriend?
\N<Kaede>Well, for now, I'll take you to those two.
\N<Kaede>I won't wait. It's your own doing, isn't it?
\N<Kaede>Because of that, we're the ones inconvenienced here.
\N<Kaede>How much of a coward are you?
\N<Kaede>You came to this village to escape from those two, right?

\N<Kaede>I can't let this village be inconvenienced because of you.
That's why I'm taking you with me.

\N<Naoto>W-Well, it's fine, isn't it? If we all go together, there
shouldn't be any danger, right?
\N<Naoto>Thank you, Kaede! Let's go to where those two are!
